1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:37,759
Miss Rulan.

3
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:38,560
Is there anything else?

4
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:40,039
I've survived in this city

5
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:42,119
thanks to the Yehu Gang's

6
00:00:42,119 --> 00:00:43,359
secret help.

7
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:45,039
Please accept my gratitude.

8
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:45,640
(Feng Da)
No.

9
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:46,280
(Yehu Gang Leader)
Don't.

10
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:49,759
Mr. Liu has helped us for years.

11
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:53,000
This is a small token of my thanks.

12
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:55,039
What do you take me for?

13
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:58,960
Give this to the victims' families.

14
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,320
I'm leaving.

15
00:01:09,060 --> 00:01:13,020
=Episode 6=

16
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,400
Master.

17
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,000
Mr. Wang warned the Yehu Gang.

18
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:22,680
Lin Rulan tricked Xin
into killing Jia Yi.

19
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,439
She thinks she has leverage over me.

20
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:26,040
In that case,

21
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:29,000
it's time to use her parents.

22
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,239
Insolent peasants!

23
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:37,959
How dare you spread rumors about nobles!

24
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:39,680
Your daughter,

25
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,719
Lin Rulan, died three years ago.

26
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,200
The whole city saw her jump.

27
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:48,079
You buried her yourselves!

28
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,959
You canceled her household register.
Am I right?

29
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,640
Y-yes, Your Honor.

30
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:55,040
But I saw her
with my own eyes yesterday!

31
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,560
You're just guilty and hallucinating.

32
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,359
You saw a ghost.

33
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:01,239
That's impossible!

34
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,439
Ghosts are cold.

35
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:04,959
Humans have warm bodies.

36
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,239
Where's your proof and witness?

37
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,400
I have a witness!

38
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,840
My wife is the witness.

39
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:12,080
My daughter is the proof.

40
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,039
I can take you to her!

41
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,840
A relative's testimony is invalid.

42
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:16,879
It doesn't count.

43
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,840
Proof?

44
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,840
How dare you!

45
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:24,000
You want me to dig up a grave with you?

46
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,439
No, Your Honor!

47
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,719
My ungrateful daughter

48
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:28,960
is at Jingyuan Manor right now!

49
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,719
Come with me to the manor,

50
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,879
and you'll see her.

51
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:36,479
You expect me to trespass on royal land?

52
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,080
You wanted proof.

53
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,240
My daughter is the proof!

54
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:44,120
Jingyuan Manor is imperial land.

55
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:46,599
We have no right to enter.

56
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:49,520
But she's living there!

57
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,479
Such malicious intent!

58
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,520
Guards!

59
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,680
Throw them in the dungeon!

60
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,120
Your Honor!

61
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:55,680
We're innocent!

62
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,199
Your Honor!

63
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:58,280
We're innocent, Your Honor!

64
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,800
Xiaojiu, keep watch outside.

65
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:00,439
Yes.

66
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,879
Your parents are acting recklessly.

67
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:08,439
They'll get Magistrate Yu in trouble.

68
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,000
They won't survive the dungeon.

69
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,439
As their daughter,

70
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:15,240
I'll do one last thing for them.

71
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:18,280
Mr. Liu, please rescue them.

72
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:22,000
Alright.

73
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:31,240
I hope he makes it in time.

74
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,479
Such good food.

75
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,039
Is this our last meal?

76
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:46,639
You have Lin Rulan to thank for this.

77
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,919
That's why you're eating well.

78
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:51,159
Doesn't look like it.

79
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:53,639
Whatever, let's eat first.

80
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:54,319
Let's go.

81
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:06,840
Mr. Wang.

82
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,159
I know.

83
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:10,199
My daughter is the Prince's concubine.

84
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,639
We'll be out soon.

85
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:14,039
Be nice to us in here.

86
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,360
When we get out,

87
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,600
my daughter

88
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,240
will make you rich and promote you.

89
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,600
Thanks in advance then.

90
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:24,319
That brat.

91
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:24,959
She actually

92
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:26,920
did something right for once.

93
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,319
Old fool.

94
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,800
Shut your mouth.

95
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,439
Master is merciful to spare your lives.

96
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,519
Got it?

97
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,000
This stitch is too straight.

98
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:58,560
Like this, loop it around here.

99
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,040
Master.

100
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,959
It's done.

101
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:20,160
The couple has been silenced.

102
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,519
But I don't understand.

103
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,800
They can't speak anymore.

104
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,120
How will they identify her?

105
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,560
People who can't speak

106
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:32,040
have their own uses.

107
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:39,740
(Jingyuan Manor)

108
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,800
Such beautiful scenery.

109
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:49,120
It feels like being there.

110
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,800
I pride myself on my embroidery skills

111
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,000
and ability to stitch anything.

112
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:53,439
But after seeing this painting,

113
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:56,279
I know I have my limits.

114
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,040
It was that year

115
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,839
when I traveled with the Prince

116
00:05:58,839 --> 00:06:00,120
and saw this scenery.

117
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,360
Now that I'm older,

118
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,279
I don't like traveling far.

119
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,439
Look at these mountains.

120
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,879
Perfectly balanced,

121
00:06:07,879 --> 00:06:09,040
eternally unchanged.

122
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,959
Unlike a young girl's beauty.

123
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:12,439
A bud today,

124
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:15,720
tomorrow, it blooms for another.

125
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,639
What do you know?

126
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:22,600
I don't, Your Highness.

127
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:24,319
But I think

128
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:26,000
any scenery becomes beautiful

129
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,560
when you pass through it.

130
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:29,240
You make it new.

131
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,800
It's spring now.

132
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:36,040
Would you like to go for a walk?

133
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,439
Even the best scenery

134
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:41,240
is boring without company.

135
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,720
I'd be honored to accompany you.

136
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,680
I'll go with you.

137
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:49,040
Spring is beautiful outside the city.

138
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:52,040
It'd be a shame to miss it.

139
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:57,839
Your Highness,
Lady Cheng'en just arrived.

140
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,720
She had that incident a few days ago.

141
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:02,319
Let her join your walk.

142
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,959
Alright.

143
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,720
Then send for Ruoheng.

144
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,279
We can relax together.

145
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,639
We messed up.

146
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,959
He invited the Princess Consort out

147
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:15,959
to do his dirty work outside the city.

148
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,800
(Li Xiaoshou, Yehu Gang)
What can he do?

149
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:18,959
Just thinking about him

150
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:19,959
makes my blood boil.

151
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,879
I refuse to believe

152
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,680
we can't find evidence against him.

153
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,199
You're a lock-picking genius.

154
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:25,199
What's stopping you?

155
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:27,000
Why can't you get into Wu Lian's house?

156
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,360
Miss Rulan will distract him today.

157
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,399
Xiaoshou,

158
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,439
try again.

159
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,279
What? Your insider

160
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,600
found no clues at all?

161
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,079
Wu Lian is cunning and careful.

162
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:37,160
He hides his tracks well.

163
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:40,040
Getting that list won't be easy.

164
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,399
I knew it.

165
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,319
Leave it to my lightning fingers.

166
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,040
I'll handle it.

167
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,160
See you later.

168
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,360
So you're saying

169
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,040
Miss Rulan is in danger today?

170
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:57,839
It's an honor to be out
with Your Highness.

171
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:59,680
I'm truly grateful.

172
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:02,240
I haven't left Jinxiu City in ages.

173
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:06,439
Even the bells sound lovely today.

174
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:08,120
You chose a perfect spot, Wenyue.

175
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:11,199
The mountains calm the mind.

176
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,639
A peaceful mind

177
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,000
makes everything better.

178
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,879
No worries, no troubles,

179
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:17,759
that's the good life.

180
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:20,959
But peace is rare.

181
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,680
Lady Cheng'en.

182
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,279
There is fresh fruit on that tree.

183
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,360
They smell delicious.

184
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,279
Try one.

185
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:30,560
Xiaotao.

186
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,879
Meng Wan went with you
to pick the fruit.

187
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,960
Where is she?

188
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,480
We split up to pick fruit.

189
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,039
I have no idea where she went.

190
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,039
Forgive me, Your Highness.

191
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,279
I met these two elders

192
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:47,240
while picking fruit.

193
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:48,960
They heard you're here

194
00:08:49,039 --> 00:08:50,720
and begged for justice.

195
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,840
Seize them!

196
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:54,440
Yes.

197
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,279
Stand down.

198
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,360
Do you know your crime?

199
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,740
(I came to see my daughter at the manor)

200
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:18,420
(But she acted like a stranger)

201
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,720
Wu Lian.

202
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:27,360
They claim

203
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:30,440
their daughter was an embroiderer
at Yanyu Embroidery House.

204
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,879
Do you know them?

205
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,559
No, Your Highness.

206
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,440
I've taken in many embroiderers
over the years.

207
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,240
There are so many.

208
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:41,399
I never ask about their backgrounds.

209
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,399
How would I know their parents?

210
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,320
What does this mean?

211
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:51,440
They mean you look like their daughter.

212
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,679
Her name is

213
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,200
Lin Rulan.

214
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:55,679
No.

215
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,039
He clearly means

216
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,399
Ruoheng is their daughter.

217
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:04,320
Ruoheng, do you know them?

218
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,120
How can you say that?

219
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:09,399
Don't you remember Lord Cheng'en,
my father?

220
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,440
Ever since I came to Jinxiu City,

221
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,559
people have been saying I'm not myself.

222
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:14,720
Then who am I?

223
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,639
Calm down, Lady Cheng'en.

224
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:20,000
They must miss their daughter dearly,

225
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:21,759
so they mistook you for her.

226
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:25,120
Just send them away.

227
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:28,080
Don't ruin our spring outing.

228
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:29,480
Your Highness,

229
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:33,440
it is said
that after Lady Cheng'en arrived,

230
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,679
Lin Rulan's ghost entered her body

231
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:36,600
and took control.

232
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,399
Ridiculous!

233
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,519
Ms. Meng,

234
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:43,200
you seem to believe I'm not myself.

235
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,759
Forgive me, Lady Cheng'en.

236
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:47,320
Jingyuan Manor's reputation matters.

237
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:49,960
It matters to everyone here.

238
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:53,039
So any old couple can claim

239
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,600
to be my parents?

240
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,840
Wenyue.

241
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:58,440
They're bullying me
because I'm an outsider.

242
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,320
Ms. Meng means well.

243
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,200
And soon, Lady Cheng'en

244
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,960
won't be an outsider anymore.

245
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,360
Your Highness.

246
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,840
Since we're free today,

247
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,080
let's question these two elders.

248
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,639
Just for fun, like a story.

249
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,440
You're overstepping.

250
00:11:19,399 --> 00:11:22,000
They said their daughter's spirit

251
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:24,519
is inside Lady Cheng'en's body.

252
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,279
Enough!

253
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:29,639
It's not them telling stories.

254
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,480
It's you, Ms. Meng.

255
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:34,559
You seem very close to them.

256
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,120
You're practically reading their minds.

257
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,159
Meng Wan and Lin Rulan

258
00:11:39,159 --> 00:11:40,720
were sworn sisters.

259
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:43,840
It's normal
that she knows their parents.

260
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,279
Exactly.

261
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,759
Meng Wan.

262
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:52,360
Does Ruoheng look like Lin Rulan?

263
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:55,360
Wenyue, I was having a great day.

264
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:57,519
Don't ruin it with a dead person.

265
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,639
Ever since I came to Jinxiu City,

266
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,159
everyone thinks I'm a dead woman.

267
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:05,440
Master Wu has no proof,

268
00:12:05,639 --> 00:12:07,000
yet he keeps harassing me.

269
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,440
Do you doubt me,

270
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:11,960
or this jade token?

271
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:16,039
Do you doubt Lord Cheng'en's family?

272
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:19,720
Or are you plotting
against Jingyuan Manor?

273
00:12:20,679 --> 00:12:21,480
Am I in your way?

274
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,600
Is that it?

275
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:25,320
Ruoheng, we're just listening
to a story.

276
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:27,080
That's all.

277
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,519
I've heard enough stories.

278
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:31,720
If Master Wu has no real proof,

279
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,759
he'll answer to me.

280
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,360
Your Highness.

281
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,200
There's an ancient method

282
00:12:37,519 --> 00:12:38,639
to test kinship.

283
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,639
Blood kinship test?

284
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:41,759
Exactly.

285
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,879
Since Lady Cheng'en takes this seriously,

286
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:49,720
let's play along and find out.

287
